{"tid":2218190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世jj]想講下個澳門自由行圍爐post同隔離登圍爐post","createTime":"2020-09-26T04:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T05:21:29.000Z","uid":227445,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"952245c9e09999322d8f48b4c3bb5830f2fcae1e","tid":2218190,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"澳門自由行post同隔離登圍爐post<br />\n其實好似樣 手法可以話係抄隔離登post<br />\n兩個都係同幾個人一齊圍爐<br />\n但圍爐同時滲啲堅料 阿媽係女人個啲<br />\n又會認同一啲衰野 小鬧大幫忙個type<br />\n等唔知路既信呢個post真係討論 繼而信曬所有野/部份野<br />\n同時打稻草人<br />\n隔離登就屌連登仔黃絲 呢邊就屌唔願承認乜乜乜<br />\n有啲真心膠落搭已經成功咗一部份 你入去為屌佢都一樣<br />\n就算無人信都已經係兩登製造左言論<br />\n啲中國媒體都圖已cap<br />\n可以好似佢地cap fb圖咁cap晒自己要既野<br />\n再話咩&quot;X登都開始有黃屍醒乜乜柒柒咁&quot;<br />\n你ban9佢又用言論自由 唔願接受 獨裁乜乜乜咁兇返你<br />\n事實係中國人同共產黨一路都用言論自由黎攻擊言論自由/文明國家<br />\n大使館都夠膽出fake news去攻擊誣衊其他國家<br />\n<br />\n我朋友建議係好似以前咁用8964等洗板/最好唔撚理"},{"pid":"ef7eb5276bd2c0ac0dd71ad792363bb10f3ada50","tid":2218190,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f83373d806345ff1342f3957315678abe3d694","tid":2218190,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556d5e9038050c9f677c17b369d48ec4da97d443","tid":2218190,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0c78038a23caf20bd6ef3dba50347dfd706e68","tid":2218190,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87525df9f3f279514a6c9fbf1daa53a074581069","tid":2218190,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" c